# Automation Exercise Selenium Project

## Project Overview
This project automates test scenarios for https://automationexercise.com using Selenium WebDriver.

## Tools Used
- Java
- Selenium WebDriver
- TestNG
- Maven
- Eclipse
- GitHub

## Test Cases Automated
1. Login
2. Logout
3. Contact Us
4. Add To Cart
5. Brand Filter
6. Category Filter
7. Product Quantity

## Project Structure
- src/test/java/testcases
- pom.xml
- testng.xml

